1. *Poljubio* je svoju devojku ispred bioskopa. (He kissed his girlfriend in front of the cinema.)
2. Ona ga je *poljubila* u obraz kao pozdrav. (She kissed him on the cheek as a greeting.)
3. Kada se vratio kući, *poljubio* je svoju majku. (When he came home, he kissed his mother.)
4. Prošle nedelje sam se *poljubila* sa svojim dečkom na plaži. (Last week I kissed my boyfriend on the beach.)
5. Zbog velike sreće, *poljubila* je svoju najbolju prijateljicu. (Due to great happiness, she kissed her best friend.)
6. *Poljubi* me pre nego što odeš. (Kiss me before you leave.)
7. On je bio toliko srećan kada ga je ona *poljubila*. (He was so happy when she kissed him.)
8. Bilo je čudno što su se *poljubili* na javnom mestu. (It was strange that they kissed in a public place.)
9. Nisam imala srca da mu kažem da ne želim da se *poljubimo*. (I didn't have the heart to tell him I didn't want to kiss him.)
10. Kada smo se *poljubili*, znao sam da je ona prava. (When we kissed, I knew she was the one.)